Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:16.91,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Shiina Mashiro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.77,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A master painter...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:23.17,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:23.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:30.63,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:34.51,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,My shower scenes lack \Nsexiness, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.72,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:39.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're talking about your manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No, not the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:44.63,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad as a love scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:47.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really look that sexy right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:49.24,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?! Get what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:54.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait. Where are you going?! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:56.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,To my room to continue drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving the shower like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:00.72,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline for the New \NArtist Award isn't far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:04.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least  \Nrespond to what I said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:07.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your room \Nand work on your manu—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.81,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Man... Manicotti?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:17.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Forget I said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:19.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're weird, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:27.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one that needs to work hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:02.99,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1250,1)}#03 So Close And Yet So Far...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.98,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you several times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for Kamiigusa \NMisaki to work in a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.21,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,She's the type to suddenly \Ndraw up storyboards...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:18.52,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in her head and start animating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.78,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,And another thing:\N I'm not Misaki's manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.25,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so please don't send me work for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.22,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.60,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's some expression \Nyou've got. Constipated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.12,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think I was voiding\N something critical,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,considering how smooth my \Ndaily bowel movements are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.99,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.70,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be in serious trouble if you \Nwere expelling love or dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.42,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That was a producer \Nfrom an anime studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:04.14,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Said they want to give Misaki a \Nbetter script for her next project.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:10.25,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, my scripts \Ndon't measure up to her talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.29,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if they need to \Ntell me that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.27,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sorata, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:34.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's amazing, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.06,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.73,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're bothered by the fact \Nthat the girl you thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.23,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,couldn't do a thing without you is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.65,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a world-renowned master painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.68,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the only one who \Ndoesn't have anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in all of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina has her manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai has her anime, \Nand you have your scripts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:12.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even Akasaka works as a programmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.25,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,You have received a \Nmessage from Company S.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.25,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,You have received a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call them goals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.16,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe just what you want to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:23.09,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The only one in Sakura Hall, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.84,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're moving out \Nof Sakura Hall, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.48,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is that "Escape from \NSakura Hall!" banner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you hung in your room a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.14,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Goal: Escape from Sakura Hall!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:38.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna return to the \Nregular dorms for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.02,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:45.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I find an \Nowner for the cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.74,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't really been \Nlooking lately, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:52.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I've got my hands \Nfull taking care of Shiina—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.20,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.58,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this off your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:57.58,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Is there still something \Nholding you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.59,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, don't place the \Nblame on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.18,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of \NMashiro-chan and the cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.24,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:25.25,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, start by deciding...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,where you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.27,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:30.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be able to decide \Nwhat you want to do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.91,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of listening to you \Npretending you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}will{\i0} leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.46,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find someone to take the cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.91,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're still just a kid if \Nyou take your anger out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.02,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,on kouhai who are down in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.06,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.06,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better follow up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.53,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Game Design Audition\N{\b0}Your big chance to turn\N your idea into a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.53,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}Our panel of judges includes prominent figures \Nfrom the game industry and designers \Nfrom major game companies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:22.96,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Akasaka, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:29.65,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Sure, I just \Nfinished checking my motion control engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.38,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: There's something \NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.85,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: About making games?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:44.48,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: How did you know that?!\N\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Because you're in the \Nmiddle of reading a website about making games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"Because you're in the middle of reading...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a website about making games"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:46.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you start by telling \Nme how someone holed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:49.44,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the next room can\N possibly know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.53,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Why don't you start by telling me how \Nsomeone holed up in the next room can possibly know that?! \N\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: What answer is there, other than hacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"What answer is there, other than hacking?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing to brag about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.70,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: That's nothing to brag about! \N\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I'mma hacking (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.12,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: That's even worse!\N\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: So, what do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.26,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,"What do I need to do to \Nbecome a game creator?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.43,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,"Actually,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:22.96,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Actually, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.96,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Actually, never mind.\N\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I see. I'm logging off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:26.90,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: Actually, never mind.\N\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I see. I'm logging off then.\N\N{\i1}Ryunosuke-sama has logged out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:42.79,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Looking for Owners{\b0}\NPlease contact Kanda Sorata in Class 2-1 for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.50,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking for owners, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So, you've finally decided to move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "finally"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.55,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some. I'll go \Nput them up over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.23,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:58.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did something good happen to Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.92,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Must have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.46,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ask the Swimming \NClub if they want some cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finished already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:15.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I found someone who wants \Nto take the cats, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:21.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the cats' owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who needs an owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanda-kun, what do you mean by "owner"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Shiina needs someone \Nto take care of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:30.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,because she's not used to attending \Na Japanese high school yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.15,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:34.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.43,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can you confess your \Nfeelings to him so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.85,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's somewhere I want \Nto go this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, that's what you meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:46.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy looking for an owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:53.57,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:01.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Kanda-kun, are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to be sure about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.69,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.59,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.15,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, kouhai-kun, get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:20.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,M-My underwear! Something's going to pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.07,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I mind a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:27.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:32.35,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this ruckus on a Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.63,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron and Jin are going on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if they go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.90,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,They said they're going \Nto a love hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A l-love hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:44.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,A hotel for couples?! A{\i1} love{\i0} hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! One of {\i1}those {\i0}love hotels!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care if \NMashiron cheats on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:50.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:56.95,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they just went to \Nget material for her manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.03,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys making such a big fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe that \Nplayboy Jin-san would go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:04.12,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,all the way to a love \Nhotel and not try anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.83,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's pretty certain \NMitaka will do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? It's as certain as...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.69,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the bullet train's arrival schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.94,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, get dressed and \Nmeet me at the front door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there in 60 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.45,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Make it 30!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.68,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll be celebrating tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:33.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the change!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.48,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow, kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Disengage your limiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Take the weights off your arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What am I training for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:57.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going as fast as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:12:00.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I still have three more \Nstages of transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,This is why earthlings are no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So, you really {\i1}are{\i0} an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They're nearby, so let's be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.79,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Shiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.79,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the stalking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.79,Saku-overlap,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the stalking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.63,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,10 meters to Mashiro-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.40,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,10 meters to Mashiro-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.44,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Locked on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:46.37,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, is this how they're \Ngetting their material?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, that's because \Nyou're not paying attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say that twice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, I can't take any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.53,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stop that. You're going \Nto make me hurl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But! But! I can't help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.63,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My overwhelming feelings \Nare about to bubble over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to \Ndo if they notice us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pretend we just \Nhappened to run into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not much of a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:24.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aoyama, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I work here on Sundays, \Nafter going to training school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really? As amazing as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.95,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.37,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You look wonderful in your uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.62,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's hide together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kamiigusa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:39.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanda-kun, you're getting too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.70,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Which one would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.05,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This one is cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.85,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to keep it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:51.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're joking. \NIt's a birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:51.76,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,For who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:56.31,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Someone close, and yet so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.41,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, one of these, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,They bought something, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me. \NI need to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My break's over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:31.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. Work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.83,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'd work hard even if \Nyou didn't tell me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.27,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.62,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My chest hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:57.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it contagious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:05.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to be the one \Nwho looks after Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:13.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think pretty, \Nquiet girls are Jin-san's type?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.96,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:19.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Fuuka-chan, \Nthe first girl he dated, was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:23.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You've been stalking him \Nsince the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I would have known even if I hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:32.32,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I never the \None standing next to Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They really came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:51.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are they seriously going inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, we have to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:06.64,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:09.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:17.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:33.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.28,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:47.93,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Am I lying on your lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.79,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:01.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Say that like it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.82,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, don't say it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just let people lie in your lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:09.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot to think about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Where's Jin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.65,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.72,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,He told me it was just like he planned, \Nand that you'd take care of me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Just like he planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:24.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did he know we were stalking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:30.82,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:31.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand our situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:35.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're a man and a woman \Nin a love hotel room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.90,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:39.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand at all, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:46.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to think a little \Nmore before you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to \Ndo if you come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.42,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with a guy and something happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I think more, I only \Ncame here for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:56.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.82,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This is necessary to be able to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.14,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:03.84,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.81,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.96,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find someone to take the cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:35.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:43.35,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of life have you \Nbeen living up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.33,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I drew pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.64,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I drew pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:55.30,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.46,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant to let you get a punch in,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.04,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but my reflexes didn't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.92,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Office Lady Rumi-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please go back to Sakura Hall today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.00,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see Misaki-senpai \Nlike this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You had to go and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:21.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's can't it be Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:23.94,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:24.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.29,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,When I see her looking all depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:32.19,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do her like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:38.87,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, enough about me. \NHow's Mashiro-chan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:43.23,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,In your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping in the bed by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:45.74,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:48.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sandwiched between the \Nshoe rack and the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.83,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Did you guys fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't even a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I took an instant kill combo, \Nand it was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:04.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's crazy, and none\N of my common sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:11.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,got through to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:16.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But Shiina didn't care \Nabout any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:23.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,and now, drawing manga \Nare everything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say she \Nhas no uncertainties...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:32.04,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-chan told me today that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.63,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,she came to Japan to \Nbecome a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.91,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,When I told her that \Nwas a waste, considering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:41.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the praise her talents had \Nearned her as a painter,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:43.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she said she didn't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:46.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.81,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:58.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But, thanks to Shiina, \Nmy eyes are finally open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:05.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll decide for myself \Nwhere I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:11.76,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw you one hell \Nof a farewell party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:13.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:48.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:57.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:04.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I really was the one \Nwho didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you ask me, \NI promise I'll go out with you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.47,0:23:14.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with the New Artist Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:15.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:16.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:19.65,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving Sakura Hall, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What color are my panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:41.06,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,#04   A World of Changing Colors
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:38.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert! How dare you \Nask me something so dirty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:40.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to imagine them either!
